and Zhiyuan left the country.

340
00:18:47,270 --> 00:18:48,899
But you actually bewitched Zhiyuan

341
00:18:48,900 --> 00:18:50,570
and made him betray me.

342
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,050
Let me ask you something.

343
00:18:54,750 --> 00:18:56,419
Do you still love him?

344
00:18:56,420 --> 00:18:57,509
Answer me.

345
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,460
Hey!

346
00:19:12,110 --> 00:19:14,250
You always knew that I loved you.

347
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:19,220
You miss her.

348
00:19:19,700 --> 00:19:21,330
I can forgive you for that.

349
00:19:22,870 --> 00:19:24,620
You investigated me on her behalf.

350
00:19:25,070 --> 00:19:25,829
I can choose

351
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:27,250
not to ask you about it.

352
00:19:29,660 --> 00:19:31,970
I can even give you my life
if you ask for it.

353
00:19:33,620 --> 00:19:35,970
If we took that flight,

354
00:19:36,350 --> 00:19:37,970
I believe

355
00:19:39,790 --> 00:19:42,140
that we'll have a happy future together.

356
00:19:43,870 --> 00:19:46,979
But why did you choose to trust her?

357
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:48,250
Why?

358
00:19:49,270 --> 00:19:50,810
Why did you choose to trust her?

359
00:19:51,220 --> 00:19:52,659
Why did you choose her instead of me

360
00:19:52,660 --> 00:19:53,970
at the very end?

361
00:20:00,070 --> 00:20:02,419
Yue, we managed to
locate Mochou's phone.

362
00:20:02,420 --> 00:20:04,000
Be ready to rescue her at any moment.

363
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:06,829
Liu, pinpoint her location.

364
00:20:06,830 --> 00:20:07,660
Yes, ma'am.

365
00:20:33,940 --> 00:20:35,619
Captain Ding, we lost the signal.

366
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:36,800
Did you manage to pinpoint it?

367
00:20:36,800 --> 00:20:37,589
Not really.

368
00:20:37,590 --> 00:20:40,050
But the area has been narrowed down
to within one km.

369
00:20:41,750 --> 00:20:43,420
This won't do. We don't have time.

370
00:20:43,830 --> 00:20:44,970
Notify everyone.

371
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:47,939
Do a sweep search within the perimeter.

372
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:48,900
Yes, ma'am.

373
00:20:50,030 --> 00:20:53,620
I bought this watch for you, you know?

374
00:20:54,270 --> 00:20:55,660
You wish to call the cops?

375
00:20:57,870 --> 00:20:59,010
Luo Yifei.

376
00:21:00,750 --> 00:21:02,380
I'll ask you one thing.

377
00:21:02,870 --> 00:21:04,860
Did you murder my sister?

378
00:21:06,700 --> 00:21:07,860
Answer me.

379
00:21:10,700 --> 00:21:11,860
Answer me!

380
00:21:12,220 --> 00:21:14,220
I didn't know that she was your sister.

381
00:21:15,460 --> 00:21:17,420
Did you do it because
Ning Jing obstructed you?

382
00:21:18,900 --> 00:21:20,939
Li Hui found out that you smuggled drugs

383
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:23,160
under the guise of international trade
using his name.

384
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:25,250
That's why he reported you
to Ning Jing in secret.

385
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:27,509
You used that to your advantage
and lured them out,

386
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:29,290
silencing everyone in the process.

387
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:32,180
Besides them,

388
00:21:32,550 --> 00:21:34,810
Li Hui, Zeng Xiang,

389
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,220
Ning Jing,

390
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:37,900
Bao Xijie,

391
00:21:38,270 --> 00:21:38,869
Xu Jun,

392
00:21:38,870 --> 00:21:42,290
Meng Zhengyi, you murdered all of them.

393
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:45,029
Lastly, you pushed all the blame
on Meng Zhengyi.

394
00:21:45,030 --> 00:21:46,029
You're truly despicable,

395
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:47,220
Luo Yifei.

396
00:21:56,420 --> 00:21:58,269
I told you not to stare at me like that.

397
00:21:58,270 --> 00:21:59,109
Don't you understand?

398
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,869
I told you not to stare at me!

399
00:22:00,870 --> 00:22:03,100
Let go of him!

400
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:10,490
What have I done wrong?

401
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:12,829
I'm making my own money here.

402
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:14,139
I didn't steal or rob anyone.

403
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,960
I tried to make money
together with them!

404
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:16,800
What have I done wrong?

405
00:22:16,800 --> 00:22:18,509
What gives them the right
to obstruct me?

406
00:22:18,510 --> 00:22:20,029
What gives?

407
00:22:20,030 --> 00:22:21,810
I gave them chances before.

408
00:22:21,870 --> 00:22:23,380
They didn't heed my advice.

409
00:22:24,550 --> 00:22:25,970
If so,

410
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:29,050
I have to get rid of them one by one.

411
00:22:30,870 --> 00:22:31,900
You lunatic.

412
00:22:31,940 --> 00:22:33,379
What did you call me?

413
00:22:33,380 --> 00:22:35,250
You're a lunatic!

414
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:37,250
That's right! I'm a lunatic!

415
00:22:37,420 --> 00:22:39,459
I've lost my mind
all because I've fallen for you!

416
00:22:39,460 --> 00:22:40,900
Did you hear me?

417
00:22:41,270 --> 00:22:41,869
Anran.

418
00:22:41,870 --> 00:22:42,810
Over here.

419
00:22:51,510 --> 00:22:52,660
Shine some light on it.

420
00:22:54,620 --> 00:22:55,810
There's a hidden compartment.

421
00:22:56,590 --> 00:22:57,419
Ms. Wei.

422
00:22:57,420 --> 00:22:59,749
We found the real blueprint
in Bao Xijie's house.

423
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:02,309
Glory Tower is actually
a twin-layered building.

424
00:23:02,310 --> 00:23:03,789
A low, hidden space was added

425
00:23:03,790 --> 00:23:05,860
between every two floors.

426
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:10,420
Everyone,
return to Glory Tower immediately.

427
00:23:18,180 --> 00:23:19,330
Li Mochou.

428
00:23:20,870 --> 00:23:22,660
Aren't you an expert at reading minds?

429
00:23:22,750 --> 00:23:24,589
Come. Take a guess.

430
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:26,330
Guess what I'm thinking right now.

431
00:23:26,790 --> 00:23:27,940
Tell me.

432
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:32,660
That's easy.

433
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:35,620
Zhiyuan chose to trust me.

434
00:23:35,870 --> 00:23:37,490
He didn't trust you.

435
00:23:37,750 --> 00:23:39,530
You thought Zhiyuan betrayed you.

436
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:41,620
That's why you tied us up
and kept us here.

437
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,770
You're just exacting revenge.

438
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:47,420
You didn't intend to let us
leave this place alive from the start.

439
00:23:47,900 --> 00:23:48,789
Am I right?

440
00:23:48,790 --> 00:23:49,940
That's right.

441
00:23:52,790 --> 00:23:53,940
Bingo.

442
00:23:54,870 --> 00:23:56,530
So what?

443
00:23:57,700 --> 00:23:59,660
Do you think anyone
is going to rescue you?

444
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:02,269
Captain Ding?

445
00:24:02,270 --> 00:24:03,899
Listen,

446
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:05,530
she won't be able to find the place.

447
00:24:05,700 --> 00:24:07,290
You have to die today.

448
00:24:12,140 --> 00:24:13,660
Ning Zhiyuan, let me ask you this.

449
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:16,080
Will you leave with me or not?

450
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:19,330
Answer me!

451
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:21,730
Scram.

452
00:24:53,070 --> 00:24:54,420
Let's play a game.

453
00:25:03,940 --> 00:25:05,100
Make a choice between you two.

454
00:25:12,900 --> 00:25:14,900
We'll definitely leave this place alive.

455
00:25:16,350 --> 00:25:17,379
Hey!

456
00:25:17,380 --> 00:25:18,530
Is anyone there?

457
00:25:44,310 --> 00:25:45,940
There's toxic gas!

458
00:25:49,550 --> 00:25:51,770
Hurry and untie the rope!

459
00:25:53,140 --> 00:25:54,140
Mochou!

460
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,250
Mochou!

461
00:26:09,550 --> 00:26:11,460
Hurry and put it on!

462
00:26:11,790 --> 00:26:13,490
Hurry and put it on!

463
00:26:15,270 --> 00:26:17,250
I can't afford to lose you!

464
00:26:18,510 --> 00:26:20,900
I've already lost Ning Jing!

465
00:26:21,030 --> 00:26:22,940
I can't afford to lose you!

466
00:26:23,790 --> 00:26:25,700
Hurry and put it on!

467
00:26:53,420 --> 00:26:54,570
Mochou.

468
00:26:55,550 --> 00:26:56,700
Here comes the oxygen tank.

469
00:26:56,940 --> 00:26:58,100
Tiaotiao.

470
00:27:01,250 --> 00:27:02,619
Captain Ding, we searched the area.

471
00:27:02,620 --> 00:27:04,659
We found no one.
I think she has escaped.

472
00:27:04,660 --> 00:27:06,530
Luo Yifei came prepared.

473
00:27:06,940 --> 00:27:07,940
Captain Ding.

474
00:27:08,830 --> 00:27:09,789
A yacht.

475
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:10,970
What?

476
00:27:13,110 --> 00:27:16,730
I gave her a yacht during her birthday.

477
00:27:16,800 --> 00:27:18,800
I haven't had the time
to transfer the ownership yet.

478
00:27:18,800 --> 00:27:20,330
That's why you guys can't find it.

479
00:27:22,980 --> 00:27:26,100
It's at Binhai Road Yacht Club.

480
00:27:26,620 --> 00:27:27,789
Captain Ding.

481
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,100
Let me join you.

482
00:27:46,750 --> 00:27:47,900
Don't move!

483
00:27:51,220 --> 00:27:52,380
Turn around!

484
00:28:08,830 --> 00:28:11,330
Did Ning Zhiyuan tell you guys
that I was here?

485
00:28:12,660 --> 00:28:14,570
He bought me this yacht, you know?

486
00:28:15,030 --> 00:28:16,180
Li Mochou,

487
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:18,900
do you think you've won?

488
00:28:19,550 --> 00:28:20,940
Listen.

489
00:28:21,380 --> 00:28:23,349
I'll never admit defeat.

490
00:28:23,350 --> 00:28:24,570
Luo Yifei.

491
00:28:25,380 --> 00:28:27,250
You've lost everything.

492
00:28:27,350 --> 00:28:28,330
That's right.

493
00:28:28,550 --> 00:28:30,220
I've lost everything indeed.

494
00:28:30,350 --> 00:28:31,730
But what gives?

495
00:28:33,270 --> 00:28:35,379
I earned all of this myself!

496
00:28:35,380 --> 00:28:37,100
No one can take them away from me!

497
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:41,900
Now, the entire yacht
has been strapped with bombs.

498
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:46,570
Do you guys dare to play a game with me?

499
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:49,140
Let's see who can survive.

500
00:28:50,420 --> 00:28:52,290
Hurry! Over there!

501
00:29:10,180 --> 00:29:12,290
