00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:53,419
Luo Yifei pushed all the blame

519
00:30:53,420 --> 00:30:55,179
on Meng Zhengyi.

520
00:30:55,180 --> 00:30:58,379
To cover up her drug manufacturing
and trafficking tracks,

521
00:30:58,380 --> 00:30:58,869
Luo Yifei

522
00:30:58,870 --> 00:31:02,620
plotted the murder of Li Hui,
ex-chairman of Tianxiang Group,

523
00:31:02,790 --> 00:31:04,829
Officer Ning Jing of Gongmen Branch,

524
00:31:04,830 --> 00:31:07,900
Zeng Xiang, suspect of Major Case 219,

525
00:31:08,550 --> 00:31:11,179
Bao Xijie, architect of Glory Tower,

